Definition: perennial south European herb having narrow entire leaves and solitary yellow flower heads and long black edible roots shaped like carrots
Synonyms: viper, s_grass, scorzonera, Scorzonera_hispanica, herb, genus_Scorzonera, m, perennial, south, European, having, narrow, entire, leaves, and, solitary, yellow, flower, heads, long, black, edible, roots, shaped, like, carrots
Category: noun.plant
